</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>韓國夫婦手機自動撥打 2000 個電話，最後發現竟是兒子惡作劇程式</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/12/a-south-korean-couples-mobile-phone-made-2000-automatic-calls-only-to-discover-their-son-was-a-prank/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=a-south-korean-couples-mobile-phone-made-2000-automatic-calls-only-to-discover-their-son-was-a-prank</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 12 Dec 2021 03:06:29 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[惡作劇]]></category><category><![CDATA[自動撥號]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1074996</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>韓國 SBS 電視台節目《世界有奇事（세상에이런일이）》近日收到一對夫妻的求助，指一家人的手機最近總是莫名其妙 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">韓國 SBS 電視台節目《世界有奇事（세상에이런일이）》近日收到一對夫妻的求助，指一家人的手機最近總是莫名其妙地自動撥打電話，2 個月內已超過 2000 通，手機甚至會自動輸入咒罵字句。在攝製組安裝鏡頭監察後，竟發現是兒子的惡作劇。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/263389138_563512594721958_327593689534936443_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1075004" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/263389138_563512594721958_327593689534936443_n-694x373.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="373" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/263389138_563512594721958_327593689534936443_n-694x373.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/263389138_563512594721958_327593689534936443_n-1280x688.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/263389138_563512594721958_327593689534936443_n-768x413.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/263389138_563512594721958_327593689534936443_n-1536x825.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/263389138_563512594721958_327593689534936443_n-2048x1100.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/263389138_563512594721958_327593689534936443_n.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1074998 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/F2479A04-FEC2-43A3-9AED-F4342022EBA7-694x381.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/F2479A04-FEC2-43A3-9AED-F4342022EBA7-694x381.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/F2479A04-FEC2-43A3-9AED-F4342022EBA7-1280x703.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/F2479A04-FEC2-43A3-9AED-F4342022EBA7-768x422.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/F2479A04-FEC2-43A3-9AED-F4342022EBA7-1536x844.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/F2479A04-FEC2-43A3-9AED-F4342022EBA7-2048x1126.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/F2479A04-FEC2-43A3-9AED-F4342022EBA7.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">韓國夫婦在節目中表示，指他們和兒子的手機經常無故自動撥出電話給不同的人，累計超過 2000 通，包括親友、小食店、餐館等。他們亦嘗試過找電訊商和手機維修商進行檢查，始終找不到問題原因，即使換上新手機也持續有一樣的情況。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">除了不停自動撥打電話之外，兒子更表示手機會自己打開訊息頁面，然後輸入咒罵的字句，十分嚇人。該對夫婦因此患上失眠症，「就算吃了安眠藥也睡不著，因為擔心電話會被隨時撥打」，飽受精神壓力。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1074999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4FE5B92C-BF26-42BA-AC44-B938EEE34831-694x388.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4FE5B92C-BF26-42BA-AC44-B938EEE34831-694x388.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4FE5B92C-BF26-42BA-AC44-B938EEE34831-1280x715.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4FE5B92C-BF26-42BA-AC44-B938EEE34831-768x429.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4FE5B92C-BF26-42BA-AC44-B938EEE34831-1536x858.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4FE5B92C-BF26-42BA-AC44-B938EEE34831-2048x1144.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/4FE5B92C-BF26-42BA-AC44-B938EEE34831.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1075000" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0EE46D1C-0ACA-4828-BCBA-25544E2A2D5F-694x384.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0EE46D1C-0ACA-4828-BCBA-25544E2A2D5F-694x384.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0EE46D1C-0ACA-4828-BCBA-25544E2A2D5F-1280x709.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0EE46D1C-0ACA-4828-BCBA-25544E2A2D5F-768x425.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0EE46D1C-0ACA-4828-BCBA-25544E2A2D5F-1536x851.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0EE46D1C-0ACA-4828-BCBA-25544E2A2D5F-2048x1134.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0EE46D1C-0ACA-4828-BCBA-25544E2A2D5F.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">攝製組到訪夫婦住所，在屋內安裝攝影機監察手機的情況。攝製組發現每次手機撥號時都是兒子率先發現，且每次手機出現問題前都在兒子手上，因此懷疑事件和兒子有關。其後攝製組請來韓國友石大學心理系教授和兒子進行對談，兒子最終承認自己就是事件的始作俑者。他覺得自己一無是處，唯獨對編寫手機程式感興趣，於是在父母手機安裝操控程式，只想跟他們開玩笑。夫婦在得知真相後崩潰落淚，兒子亦透過節目向所有受害者道歉。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_82923"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iXJijaRoyxY?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://youtu.be/iXJijaRoyxY">YouTube</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
