</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>智能手機可伸縮相機鏡頭  OPPO 官方宣佈將發表新產品</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/12/oppo-self-developed-retractable-camera/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=oppo-self-developed-retractable-camera</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 12 Dec 2021 03:05:45 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[Inno day]]></category><category><![CDATA[oppo]]></category><category><![CDATA[伸縮式鏡頭]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1075174</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>OPPO 日前釋出預告片，展示一部未公佈手機將擁有伸縮式鏡頭設計。官方表示，即將推出的伸縮鏡頭不但可以防水，更有 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">OPPO 日前釋出預告片，展示一部未公佈手機將擁有伸縮式鏡頭設計。官方表示，即將推出的伸縮鏡頭不但可以防水，更有手機墜落的保護設計，該技術將會在 12 月 14 日公佈更多內容。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1075176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C53302C1-B277-4B76-817A-7A9C62E165DF-694x358.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="358" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C53302C1-B277-4B76-817A-7A9C62E165DF-694x358.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C53302C1-B277-4B76-817A-7A9C62E165DF-1280x660.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C53302C1-B277-4B76-817A-7A9C62E165DF-768x396.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C53302C1-B277-4B76-817A-7A9C62E165DF-1536x792.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C53302C1-B277-4B76-817A-7A9C62E165DF.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">OPPO 這種新的「彈出式」相機創意模仿了舊傻瓜相機的可伸縮鏡頭，只需輕按一下相機按鈕，鏡頭就會從手機表面升起。這套 OPPO 表示屬「自主研發」的伸縮式鏡頭，將搭載 1/1.56&#8243; 感光元件和 50mm 等效焦距 F2.4 光圈鏡頭，貌似是以伸出鏡頭的方式來改善手機上光學變焦的效果，加上鏡頭的感光元件稍大，便透過伸縮鏡頭方式使鏡頭在收納時更為小巧。此設計可提供更好的移動長焦功能，又不會增加手機相機凸起的尺寸或佔用手機機身內部的大量空間，另一方面亦可在不影響質量的情況下為主攝像頭和長焦攝像頭使用相同的感測器；此外，伸縮鏡不但可以防水，在探測到跌落時會自動收縮，避免鏡頭因手機墮落而損壞。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1075177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/00E14E29-A211-45EC-9964-C432E8348C99-694x547.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="547" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/00E14E29-A211-45EC-9964-C432E8348C99-694x547.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/00E14E29-A211-45EC-9964-C432E8348C99-1142x900.jpeg 1142w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/00E14E29-A211-45EC-9964-C432E8348C99-768x605.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/00E14E29-A211-45EC-9964-C432E8348C99-1536x1210.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/00E14E29-A211-45EC-9964-C432E8348C99.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1075178" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0AE24DFF-2D62-439C-A08E-B0A0CE1E699E-662x580.jpeg" alt="" width="662" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0AE24DFF-2D62-439C-A08E-B0A0CE1E699E-662x580.jpeg 662w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0AE24DFF-2D62-439C-A08E-B0A0CE1E699E-1027x900.jpeg 1027w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0AE24DFF-2D62-439C-A08E-B0A0CE1E699E-768x673.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0AE24DFF-2D62-439C-A08E-B0A0CE1E699E-1536x1346.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0AE24DFF-2D62-439C-A08E-B0A0CE1E699E.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 662px" /></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Most pop-ups are annoying&#8230;</p><p>But not our self-developed retractable camera!  😉</p><p>Explore more in INNO WORLD on 14/12.<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/OPPOINNODAY2021?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#OPPOINNODAY2021</a> <a href="https://t.co/33hgJSw8If">pic.twitter.com/33hgJSw8If</a></p><p>&mdash; OPPO (@oppo) <a href="https://twitter.com/oppo/status/1468143243183468556?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 7, 2021</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">OPPO 將於 12 月 14 及 15 日，一連兩日舉行 Inno Day，展示廠商的創新科技，而這個伸縮式鏡頭將會是其中之一，屆時將會有更多資料公開。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/oppo/status/1468143243183468556?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1468143243183468556%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Foppo-E9A090E5918AE998B2E6B0B4-E998B2E8B78CE890BDE79A84E4BCB8E7B8AEE5BC8FE79BB8E6A99F-101412640.html">Twitter</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
